## Amazon Q MCP Server Setup

This project uses a lightweight Kubernetes MCP server through Amazon Q's `uvx` CLI:

json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "kubernetes-mcp-server": {
      "command": "uvx",
      "args": ["kubernetes-mcp-server@latest"],
      "env": {
        "FASTMCP_LOG_LEVEL": "ERROR"
      }
    }
  }
}
